Transcription.Text: "My goodness, look at those women planting things, isn't it primitive?" "About ten-o'clock, I suppose, the old tyme stuff." In spite of all the transferred maternity she was endowed with by her patients, poor serena was an infant-in-arms as a buyer of property.
